{"tid":367752,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"半秃李修賢踎街邊　食相好麻甩","createTime":"2017-08-21T03:56:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-30T05:27:01.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e42ef87b6869c1470ab93fa0c05bce308ca026c4","tid":367752,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T03:56:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=a_AMxBhFXBQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Da_AMxBhFXBQ&d=gaqVBlAyGboJEH5G65GD%2BDQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=c1f334c3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=a_AMxBhFXBQ</a><br />\n發佈日期：2017年8月20日<br />\n飾演警察深入民心的李修賢，圈中個個都叫他「李Sir」。近年他主力返大陸拍劇，香港少見露面。<br />\n<br />\n今年65歲的他，6月與麥包拍網劇《4度望遠鏡》，當時他西裝骨骨現身，雖然身形稍為發福，肚腩凸凸，髮線後移，但都算keep得不錯。<br />\n<br />\n人靠衣裝真是沒錯！早前一身便裝的他，與朋友到西貢西餐廳午餐，更一邊食嘢一邊吹水。可能當日他太肚餓，見他狼吞虎嚥，加埋個佬味十足的造型及半秃頭，真是麻甩味十足。"},{"pid":"1ebe891df58ac3ac4b94e671a3a3b5946f8e03a2","tid":367752,"uid":2215,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T03:58:12.000Z","msg":"都幾無聊單新聞"},{"pid":"98d471cecb7f0286b48aee748c1803c311a979f8","tid":367752,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T03:59:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"73e6f5453e8486605bdd76f51654ffa521616b20","tid":367752,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T10:56:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/entertainment/26oo9.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fzh-hk%2Fentertainment%2F26oo9.html&d=gaqVBlAyGboJEH5G65GD%2BDQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=e9e33fa3\" target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/entertainment/26oo9.html</a><br />\n好似有份逼害星爺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37fb1c8dcf618e2beb6b74783b721e50018424a5","tid":367752,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T13:29:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" cl